VAD - Voice Activity Detector

Usage:
   vad [options] -i <input-wav> -o <output-vad> [-w <output-wav>]
   vad (-h | --help)
   vad --version

Options:
   -i FILE, --input-wav=FILE   WAVE file for voice activity detection
   -o FILE, --output-vad=FILE  Label file with the result of VAD
   -w FILE, --output-wav=FILE  WAVE file with silences cleared
   -1 FILE, --alfa1=FLOAT      Marge sobre k0 per determinar el llindar d'un V/S [default: 6.8]
   -2 FILE, --alfa2=FLOAT      Marge sobre P1 per determinar el llindar d'un V/S [default: 3.2]
   -V FILE, --t_voice=FLOAT    Temps mínim per considerar veu [default: 0]
   -S FILE, --t_silence=FLOAT  Temps mínim per considerar vsilencia [default: 0.15]
   -z FILE, --zcr=FLOAT        LLindar ZCR [default: 3600]
   -v, --verbose  Show debug information
   -h, --help     Show this screen
   --version      Show the version of the project
